<node TEXT="facility had two SMRs, eight Gas Chromatographs, five compressors, three dryers, two glycol / water cooling systems, four miniature SMRs (H2Gens), three 20k? LH2 tanks, two 15k and one 10k and one 50k LN2 tanks, one DI water loop, and all the support systems that revolved around it. We also had a high-pressure N2 system with a 10k tank and a LIN cryo-pump, and a high-pressure tube trailer" POSITION="right" ID="ID_962344259" CREATED="1459204102198" MODIFIED="1459210424720">
